---
layout: base.njk
title: "Joe Sheldon | Redfin Senior Agent"
permalink: /index.html
---
<main class="container">
    <section class="profile-card">
        <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="/assets/images/joe.jpg" alt="Joe Sheldon - Seattle Real Estate Agent" class="headshot">
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="name">Joe Sheldon</h1>
        <p class="title">Redfin Senior Agent</p>
        <p class="service-area">Serving North King & South Snohomish Counties, Washington</p>
        
        <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="stat-number">{{ personalStats['Closed Sales'] }}</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Transactions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="stat-number">${{ personalStats['Total Sales Volume'] }}M</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Volume</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="stat-number">{{ personalStats['Average Rating'] }}</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Average Rating</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-info">
            <p><a href="tel:2064527845">(206) 452-7845</a></p>
            <p><a href="mailto:joe.sheldon@redfin.com">joe.sheldon@redfin.com</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="/contact.vcf" class="btn btn-secondary">Save My Contact Info</a>
            <a href="https://www.redfin.com/real-estate-agents/joe-sheldon?loyalty=true" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">View My Redfin Profile</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="profile-card events-promo">
        <h2>Free Home Buying Classes</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center; font-size: 0.95rem;">Join us to learn everything you need to know about navigating the current real estate market.</p>
        <a href="/events/" class="btn btn-primary">View Upcoming Classes & Register</a>
    </section>

    <section class="reviews">
        <h2>Client Reviews</h2>
        
        {% for review in homepageReviews %}
        <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="review-text">"{{ review['Full Review'] }}"</p>
            <div class="review-author">— {{ review.Reviewer }}</div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <section class="bio-section">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>I transplanted to Seattle in 2009, and the Pacific Northwest has become my new home. I am in love with its natural beauty and the abundance of year-round activities. Having grown up around the construction business, I developed a deep understanding of what makes a good home. My real estate passion comes from my desire to help you navigate the journey of purchasing one of the largest yet most personal items of your lifetime. I joined Redfin in 2014 to pursue this passion relentlessly. I like my customers to think of me as their coach throughout the entire process. My team and I will give you expert guidance at every turn, and I'll be by your side through the ups and downs. You can expect me to provide honest advice and tireless advocacy.</p>
    </section>
</main>